global class CustomIterable implements Iterator<Contact>{ 

   List<Contact> contacts {get; set;} 
   Integer i {get; set;} 

   public CustomIterable(){ 
       contacts = [SELECT Id,AccountId FROM Contact WHERE Is_Synced__c = false]; 
       i = 0; 		
   }   

   global boolean hasNext(){ 
       if(i >= contacts.size()) {
           return false; 
       } else {
           return true; 
       }
   }    

   global Contact next(){ 
       i++; 
       return contacts[i-1]; 
   } 
}
